Package swen221.conway.rules

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    ConwaysOverpopulationRule
    This should implements Conway's rule for overproduction: "Any live cell with more than three live neighbours dies, as if by over-population"
    ConwaysReproductionRule
    This should implement Conway's rule for reproduction: "Any dead cell with exactly three live neighbours becomes a live cell, as if by reproduction"
    ConwaysUnderpopulationRule
    This should implement Conway's rule for underproduction: "Any life cell with fewer than two live neighbors die, as if caused by under-population"
